cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.CL 

This paper is about image retrieval using deep learning and metric learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel metric learning strategy, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with information retrieval, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval). The paper also mentions large-scale datasets, which could indicate that it belongs to cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper uses entropy regularization, which could suggest that it belongs to cs.CL (Computation and Language).
